{
  "stem": "11272.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they tell me some of their problems.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they ask me some of their questions, how they could overcome their difficulties.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we somehow-- at least I give them my opinion what I think they ought to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it's so wonderful that 10, 15 years later, those same kids are successful.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They become doctors.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They become lawyers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They become business people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They'll come up to me and hug me and kiss me and tell me how grateful they are that I managed to make them realize that their problems is not the end of the world.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I could not speak about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when my daughters found out that the Catholic priest-- who later on became a cardinal, Cardinal Malone-- got me to speak in school, my children insisted that I got to come to their school.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went there and spoke to the school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I could never talk to my kids about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was about 25 years ago.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I don't know whether it was the directly related so much to the Holocaust, as it was directly related to the way my mother and father would have wanted them to be raised.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I taught them to love.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I taught them to be good people-- at least I wanted to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they turned out very good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm very proud of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my youngest daughter's working for the SEC in Washington.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My middle daughter just got remarried to a very nice young man, whose mother is a survivor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my oldest daughter-- married to a wonderful, caring person with service merchandise.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, and, and I don't think she could have ever met anybody any better than he is.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he's very good to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he's very good to her daughter.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
